<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>Palika GIS Demo Request Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f7fc;
            color: #2c3e50;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            0% {
                opacity: 0;
            }
            100% {
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }
        .email-container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease-out;
        }
        .email-header {
            background-color: #4a90e2;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 25px;
            border-top-left-radius: 8px;
            border-top-right-radius: 8px;
        }
        .email-header h2 {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .email-body {
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #34495e;
        }
        .email-body p {
            margin-bottom: 18px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        .email-body a {
            color: #4a90e2;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .email-body a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .email-footer {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #718096;
            border-bottom-left-radius: 8px;
            border-bottom-right-radius: 8px;
        }
        .email-footer a {
            color: #4a90e2;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .email-footer a:hover {
            color: #50c878;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="email-header">
            <h2>Palika GIS Demo Request Confirmation</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <p>Dear <strong><%= firstName %></strong>,</p>
            <p>Thank you for your interest in Palika GIS. We have received your request for a demo access.</p>
            <p>Your request is under review, and we will send you the login credentials soon.</p>
            <p>If you have any questions in the meantime, feel free to <a href="mailto:support@palikagis.com">contact our support team</a>.</p>
            <p>We appreciate your patience and look forward to providing you with access to our platform.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>Best regards,</p>
            <p><strong>Palika GIS Team</strong></p>
            <p><a href="mailto:support@palikagis.com">support@palikagis.com</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
